recipient and no longer protected. I understand that the specified information to be released may include, but is not limited
to: history, diagnoses, and/or treatment of drug or alcohol abuse, mental illness, or communicable disease, including Human
Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) and Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS).
I understand that treatment or payment cannot be conditioned on my signing this authorization, except in certain circumstances such as
for participation in research programs, or authorization of the release of testing results for pre-employment purposes. I understand that I may
revoke this authorization in writing at any time except to the extent that action has been taken in reliance upon the authorization. I understand I
may be charged a retrieval/processing fee and for copies of my medical records according to Texas Hospital Licensing law.
